@defvar udisks-service-type
Type for the service that runs
@uref{https://udisks.freedesktop.org/docs/latest/, UDisks}, a @dfn{disk
management} daemon that provides user interfaces with notifications and ways
to mount/unmount disks.  Programs that talk to UDisks include the
@command{udisksctl} command, part of UDisks, and GNOME Disks.  Note that
